main event: At approximately 1742 on 23 September 1963, four round objects with pale yellow lights circled low over a power line.
interesting points: The objects moved very rapidly without any visible exhaust or trail., The sighting lasted for about 45 minutes in clear sky conditions., Witnesses reported deep red elongated lights associated with the objects., The objects were described as being intelligently controlled., Eight persons including two local police were confirmed witnesses.
sighted object: four round objects with pale yellow lights
